targets.query:
import "date"
import "array"

data = [
  {time_from: date.add(d: -1h, to: now()), button_text: "1 Hour", primary: 0},
  {time_from: date.add(d: -12h, to: now()), button_text: "12 Hours", primary: 0},
  {time_from: date.add(d: -24h, to: now()), button_text: "24 Hours", primary: 0}
]

array.from(rows: data)
  |> yield()
